{"tid":1329621,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[720手工班] 護手型水樽護墊工作坊","createTime":"2019-07-18T09:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T14:24:33.000Z","uid":281488,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb2642026d47bb1a016b7f87f739c72f57cdf70","tid":1329621,"uid":281488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"承上post ：<br />\n[撐警，附教學] 強烈建議警察自製護手！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325085\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325085</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/eV7SW29.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeV7SW29.gif&h=7909cebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現連登唔少撐警巴打都紛紛表示想整，721送俾當值香港警察手足以示心意。<br />\n而今個星期六，我決定先開個工作坊....<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係教大家做護手，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而係整一款完全無關但生得一模一樣，用黎守護你心愛水樽既</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">護手型水樽護墊</span></span>，等大家可以保護你最愛既水樽，唔怕無啦啦、散散下步突然俾d 冒警痴線佬亂棍打爆！<br />\n如果大家覺得有用，不妨自製送俾親戚朋友，或將製作方法教俾偶遇既同路人，遍地開花，隨時隨地守護樽中既Water!!<br />\n<br />\n地點：尖沙咀<br />\n時間：下午2-3、3-4 兩節，視參加人數可能加開更多節<br />\n人數：每節上限20人<br />\n費用：全免，物料工具老子全包！<br />\n<br />\n今晚會公佈報名方式同將參加者加入tg group，麻煩有興趣既巴絲打參加！<br />\n由於場所限制，冒警人士與狗不得進入，不便之處敬請原諒！<br />\n唔好問自己可以為心愛既水樽做d 咩，而家就係機會！<br />\n<br />\n最後，撐警撚都係果句：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QHdiPCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHdiPCh.png&h=8c7582fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae8d326dbd541587d5685bd713a0c5db58384a2a","tid":1329621,"uid":281488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa048bbad0f7e63bd6ef04d25dc7b7d31c25e40c","tid":1329621,"uid":281488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9abf59d7e2ea753d9af11a10510